{"about_the_game":"Limbs is a one to two player dexterity game where you take control over the limbs of a string puppet. Immerse yourself in a handcrafted world where moving each limb individually makes for challenging but rewarding and hilarious gameplay. Playfully swing, jump and manually walk as best as you can through a knackered kingdom while progressing through a story inspired by puppet theater storytelling.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2>Control two limbs at a time: In single player you switch the control between arms and legs, while in two player mode both players take control over one arm and one leg.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/VaseCarry_24.gif?t=1731410621\" /><br><br>Make your limbs work together to master a unique gameplay loop: Even if the tasks you perform would be easy in another game, the coordinative nature makes them challenging.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/CrocodileChomp_24.gif?t=1731410621\" /><br><br>You choose how to move your character: Just like a real puppeteer all character motions are under your control.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2306020/extras/ChandelierSwing.gif?t=1731410621\" /><br><br>Intuitive cooperative gameplay: After a while players start to get in tune with each other and perform actions together even without communicating verbally.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Failing Forward","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2306020/835bd3bfdda0ad7a3899207543241ba5419d7372.jpg"},{"name":"Dog's Death","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2306020/6b8dfe7cacd20b71d127666da7469d762d8dd007.jpg"},{"name":"Manor Lord","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/230602